{"tid":2332690,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點看待KPOP選秀初代空降閪","createTime":"2020-12-19T20:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T11:19:36.000Z","uid":205928,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"57aaa42c15330fbc93bcb0539837ce729c948832","tid":2332690,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non9ce仲邊撚有面串izone<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJYP娛樂對於sixteen最終結果引發的爭議道歉，包括對已剔除成員Momo最後的入團資格做<br />\n出了另外的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n「我們為了最終選拔的過程不明朗而感到抱歉，在此將進一步說明細節。<br />\n<br />\nSIXTEEN最終成員的決定取決於公司人員及觀眾投票，但在最後一集倘若只選七名成員的<br />\n話會有些期望無法被達成，因此決定加入觀眾中意的成員（子瑜）和朴軫永中意的成員（<br />\nMomo）。」<br />\n<br />\nJYP繼續表示，他們虛心接受各方的指責，包括最後臨時加入兩名成員的決定、其他被指<br />\n責的議題，以及殘忍的競爭氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n「為了讓觀眾與節目更深層的連結，同時滿足節目的效果以及公司考量，我們期望大眾能<br />\n理解，未來我們將更盡力做出使大眾滿意的決策。」"},{"pid":"6673d18524aefa56cb59eeff8a2d7e8695cff546","tid":2332690,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:13:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://karenliu05.pixnet.net/blog/post/460411037-sixteen-作為觀眾而非粉絲感到生氣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkarenliu05.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F460411037-sixteen-%E4%BD%9C%E7%82%BA%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E8%80%8C%E9%9D%9E%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E6%84%9F%E5%88%B0%E7%94%9F%E6%B0%A3&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=e0b21e7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://karenliu05.pixnet.net/blog/post/460411037-sixteen-作為觀眾而非粉絲感到生氣</a>"},{"pid":"311ee68319322c68fe18eeac65e8b887e3e7a308","tid":2332690,"uid":205928,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:13:49.000Z","msg":"解散TWICE！刻不容緩！"},{"pid":"e2560cab40f22ce791bfe1d9166655bbd5723199","tid":2332690,"uid":205928,"like":16,"dislike